{p2col: 描述：}反累积指数分布，尺度为 {it:b}：如果 {cmd:exponential(}{it:b}{cmd:,}{it:x}{cmd:)} = {it:p}，则
                 {cmd:invexponential(}{it:b}{cmd:,}{it:p}{cmd:)} = {it:x}{p_end}
{p2col: 域 {it:b}：}1e-323 到 8e+307{p_end}
{p2col: 域 {it:p}：}0 到 1{p_end}
{p2col: 范围：}1e-323 到 8e+307{p_end}
